import React from 'react';
import { Container, TextField, Button, Typography } from '@mui/material';

const Contact = () => (
  <Container>
    <Typography variant="h4" component="h2" gutterBottom>
      Contact Me
    </Typography>
    <form>
      <TextField
        label="Name"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
      />
      <TextField
        label="Email"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
      />
      <TextField
        label="Message"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        multiline
        rows={4}
      />
      <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit">
        Send
      </Button>
    </form>
  </Container>
);

export default Contact;
